\lang english
6.2 Vulnerability Scoring and Prioritization
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Standard Scoring
\series default
:
 Vulnerabilities shall be assessed using the Common Vulnerability Scoring System (CVSS) v3.1 or higher.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Prioritization
\series default
:
 Remediation prioritization shall be determined by the base score and the asset's criticality classification (as defined in 
\series bold
Policy 
